        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 3. (A) Specimen of Jaspis eudermis Lévi & Vacelet, 1958 collected from the Alboran Sea and photographed on graphic paper (MNCN-Sp71-BV10). (B) Three Alboranian specimens of Hemiasterella elongata Topsent, 1928 (from left to right, MNCN-Sp66-BV21, MNCN-Sp66 B & A)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4908949/files/figure.png" .
